        "224d222f-ae90-4397-8f15-637044d5997a": {
            "category": "File",
            "categoryType": "Data",
            "id": "224d222f-ae90-4397-8f15-637044d5997a",
            "name": "pathname",
            "description": "A standard file on a filesystem mounted to the deployment machine \nIn some cases drops are created **outside** the context of a session, most notably during unit tests. In these cases the base directory is a fixed location under ``/tmp``.\nThe following table summarizes the calculation of the final path used by the ``FileDrop`` class depending on its parameters:\n============ ===================== ===================== ========== . filepath ------------ ------------------------------------------------------ dirname empty relative absolute ============ ===================== ===================== ========== **empty** /``$B``/``$u`` /``$B``/``$f`` /``$f`` **relative** /``$B``/``$d``/``$u`` /``$B``/``$d``/``$f`` **ERROR** **absolute** /``$d``/``$u`` /``$d``/``$f`` **ERROR** ============ ===================== ===================== ==========\nIn the table, ``$f`` is the value of ``filepath``, ``$d`` is the value of ``dirname``, ``$u`` is the drop's UID and ``$B`` is the base directory for this drop's session, namelly ``/the/cwd/$session_id``.",
            "x": 1504,
            "y": 375.5,
            "repositoryUrl": "",
            "commitHash": "",
            "paletteDownloadUrl": "",
            "dataHash": "",
            "parentId": null,
            "embedId": null,
